cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.AI 

This paper focuses on the security of smart devices, specifically in detecting sensor-based threats. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also utilizes machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves collecting and analyzing data, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper proposes a framework for detecting threats, which could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering).
